    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "内容层面还有些状态需要体现。博客文章可以被精选，讨论可以有已采纳的回答。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blog Post",
        "Featured",
        "Discussion",
        "Accepted Answer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "\"已采纳的回答\"是指讨论帖下的某条评论被标记为答案，还是一个独立的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discussion",
